org.jacorb.poa
Class AOM

java.lang.Object
  org.jacorb.poa.AOM

public class AOM
extends Object

This class maps object id's to servants and vice versa. A oid/servant pair can be added/removed using add(),remove(). The data can be retrieved using getServant() or getObjectId().

Author:
Reimo Tiedemann, FU Berlin
